## Pre-Testing Setup {#sec-pre-testing}

### Test Equipment Required {#sec-test-equipment}

| Equipment | Purpose | Minimum Specification |
|-----------|---------|----------------------|
| Power Supply | Probe power delivery | 5V or 12V, current-limited to 2A **(Target)** |
| Digital Multimeter | Resistance, voltage, current | 0.1% accuracy **(Target)**, 4.5 digit |
| LCR Meter | Coil inductance and Q factor | 10 kHz test frequency, 0.1% accuracy **(Target)** |
| Oscilloscope | Signal verification | 50 MHz bandwidth **(Target)**, 2-channel minimum |
| Function Generator | Signal injection testing | 1 Hz - 100 kHz **(Target)**, sine/square |
| Base Hub | System-level testing | Complete calibrated unit |

